metadata.name: Pepe Street
metadata.description: Celebrating the Power of Collective Support: My heartfelt gratitude goes out to my incredible collectors who have shown unwavering love and support. As a token of appreciation, I present my first giveaway art pieceâ€”a captivating portrayal of a Pepe frog playfully altering the Wall Street sign to read 'Pepe Street.' This whimsical artwork signifies the strength of our collective voice, emphasizing the transformative potential of unity and creative expression. Thank you for being a part of this incredible journey.
